    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3293926129" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1579077078983326217">This spring, I applied to a college where I planned to major in Talmud, got in, and legitimately almost went despite not having studied Torah since my bat mitzvah and not being entirely sure what the Talmud is. This book is that good. <br/><br/>Additionally, as much as Reuven&apos;s Jewish world is different from my own, it is so good to see Jewish characters and Jewish stories that don&apos;t revolve entirely around the Holocaust, even though it does explore its impact.<br/><br/>I tend to be a skim-reader, but I always make</span>
  <span id="freeText1579077078983326217" style="display:none">This spring, I applied to a college where I planned to major in Talmud, got in, and legitimately almost went despite not having studied Torah since my bat mitzvah and not being entirely sure what the Talmud is. This book is that good. <br /><br />Additionally, as much as Reuven's Jewish world is different from my own, it is so good to see Jewish characters and Jewish stories that don't revolve entirely around the Holocaust, even though it does explore its impact.<br /><br />I tend to be a skim-reader, but I always make sure to slow down when I read these books, because every word Potok writes is worth reading.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1579077078983326217" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


